title: Ask HN: What will Content Marketing look like in a post-AI world?
text:
Today, Content Marketing is basically just a way to drive search traffic from Google.

Will people still read corporate blog posts once AI can provide quality answers to any query?

What will Content Marketing look like once we chat instead of search?

Show HN: Open-pdf-sign, a CLI for digital PDF signing
text:
Link: https://openpdfsign.org/

Hey HN, we want to introduce you to open-pdf-sign - the open-source solution for automatically signing PDFs from your CLI.

As developers, Thomas and I (Philipp) were frustrated with the lack of options for easily signing PDFs. Most solutions were either proprietary or had restrictive licenses, making it difficult for us to use them in our projects.

That's why we decided to create open-pdf-sign - a simple, easy-to-use tool for signing PDF from your CLI. We designed it to be user-friendly for developers, with a permissive license allowing easy integration into any project.

We also added a configurator that configures your Nginx server. It will automatically install and configure your Nginx so all your PDFs will be signed with your SSL certificate on the fly. You can even use your existing Let’sEncrypt certificates.

We believe that open-pdf-sign will be a valuable tool for any developer looking to quickly sign PDFs on their webserver or with their project. Give it a try and let us know what you think!

Thomas & Philipp
